{"tid":1592143,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有聽boyz reborn 首 時代感召","createTime":"2019-09-24T12:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T13:00:15.000Z","uid":114155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd74a8e1644f9067b7a3befa137096ec464ad852","tid":1592143,"uid":114155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"呢排因爲場運動 咁岩搵到呢首歌<br />\n發現佢啲歌詞好鬼中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家可以聽下 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LxHTC3ZU7ZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLxHTC3ZU7ZY&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=5add043f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LxHTC3ZU7ZY</a><br />\n<br />\n時代在感召　牆璧中見裂痕<br />\n時代在指引　常規全然變更<br />\n抬頭望有天　夢想不再下沉　別再等<br />\n時代在呼召　雙手補救缺憾<br />\n時代像叫人　別放棄再啞忍<br />\n存活幻變中　初衷緊記勿忘　存丹心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地今日置身嘅年代　係一個物質豐裕嘅時代<br />\n時代巨輪隱約嘅存在　邊個明白身處大時代中嘅無奈<br />\n面對唔公平嘅時候　有人會選擇　沈默<br />\n係大是大非嘅面前　邊個會以身　作則<br />\n無論你係咩身份地位　擁有幾多財富資產技藝<br />\n年紀大小同肥瘦高矮　仍然可以為自己嘅夢想企出來<br />\n唔好俾現實打沉自己　唔好嘗試去睇低自己<br />\n亂世中我哋走在一起　未來就由我哋共同擔起<br />\n<br />\n有話兒　有夢語　我出走　到盡頭<br />\n地動搖 遍地雪 也不休<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3051577ff93afb1f78ca5b822b5775815273da76","tid":1592143,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"e3479012d56e279e87a6d6ff174a3484f1c34892","tid":1592143,"uid":114155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"Push 支持本地band隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}